name: Impaled
description:
Great variation of Geometry Dash!
Navigate amazing levels in this one touch platformer. Jump, fly and slide as you develop your skill and take your hero ever further. New levels and playing styles keep you constantly on the edge. This is the game all jumping games want to grow up to be!

* Levels of different speeds.
* Slow down or speed up.
* Fly like a spaceship.
* Meet penguins, horses, dinosaurs and a whale.
* Fly an airplane and go on a boat.
* Handle high speed or slow but precise jumps.
